{"tid":2452359,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"清明商機？｜內地推「墓地貸」無抵押借$23萬買陰宅 港學者：債留子孫死唔安樂","createTime":"2021-03-18T20:00:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-18T22:18:57.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb35ae98b105a44e6865fafc95c6ceda85f20f5","tid":2452359,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T20:00:53.000Z","msg":"內地除了樓價，墓地價格近年亦持續攀升，動輒數十萬元，讓不少人高呼「死不起」。內地有銀行卻從中看到商機，與雲南省昆明市的墓園合作，要在清明節推出「墓地按揭貸」，聲稱借錢買墓地不需抵押，最高可貸款20萬元人民幣 （下同，約23.9萬港元），還能分10年攤還，但年利率高達9%。銀行更稱若申請人年紀太大，可找子女、孫兒作貸款人。結果引發爭議太大，連官媒都批評牟利，墓園與涉事銀行昨午突煞停「墓地貸」。香港學者向《蘋果》指，這類無抵押貸款只是銀行巧立名目，以吸引民眾借錢。他批評「墓地貸」道德上並不可取，利用中國人想盡孝道的傳統心態，令人離世後要子孫「孭債」，「死得起，但死得唔安樂」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210319/AHOJGYVSERFZHDFCDNWEXUQEQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210319%2FAHOJGYVSERFZHDFCDNWEXUQEQY%2F&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSt2UZYMvR53lMa2%2BnKJB5b4%3D&h=f63e01de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210319%2FAHOJGYVSERFZHDFCDNWEXUQEQY%2F&h=5b24f7d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210319/AHOJGYVSERFZHDFCDNWEXUQEQY/</a>"},{"pid":"1ef86e631d5fea55cdb5d0c6e7f2af39f1ec16d9","tid":2452359,"uid":134683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T20:34:43.000Z","msg":"呢啲嘢冇省市政府配合點成事<br />\n中間仲俾唔知幾多層級夾埋一齊撈油水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7489310bcc94f986ac3a790db62a8e0640627b6","tid":2452359,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-18T20:45:13.000Z","msg":"港學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n債留子孫唔安樂？你班仆街冇資格講<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n97打後堆無形債<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7cb698d91b3aa296d93e73aeeec1f7ebaee1c4e","tid":2452359,"uid":